            <button data-close-button class="close-button">&times;</button>
        </div>
        <div class="modal-body">
            Overlook Rock Trail is a 1.6 mile moderately trafficked loop trail located near Charleston,
            West Virginia that features beautiful wild flowers and is rated as moderate. The trail is
            primarily used for hiking, walking, nature trips, and bird watching and is accessible
            year-round. Dogs are also able to use this trail but must be kept on leash.
        </div>
    </div>
